 Contact Us    UIC menu    UIC.edu    Campus Map       Search                        The Pulse           The Pulse  Welcome to The Pulse, an ePublication for Student Affairs Staff. The Pulse aims to share feature stories; spotlights on employees, departments, and programs; videos; photos; important events and due dates; recaps; staffing changes; and more. A goal of the Pulse is to provide much of the information currently provided in separate all-staff e-mails, making it easier to find what you need. The Pulse is published monthly by Student Affairs Marketing and Communications. Check out the latest issue at   The Pulse - May 2018     Read previous ePublications of The Pulse   The Pulse – April 2018  The Pulse – March 2018  The Pulse – February 2018  The Pulse – January 2018  The Pulse – December 2017  The Pulse – November 2017  The Pulse – August 2017  The Pulse – July 2017  The Pulse – June 2017  The Pulse – May 2017  The Pulse – April 2017  The Pulse – March 2017  The Pulse – February 2017  The Pulse – January 2017  The Pulse – December 2016  The Pulse – November 2016                    UIC Logo        STUDENT AFFAIRS         For Employees    SA Portal    SA Human Resources    Leave Management    SA Technology      About Us    Mission & Vision    Strategic Priorities    Annual Report    Assessment    Giving Opportunities      INITIATIVES    U & I Care    UIC Connection    UIC Impact        BUTTON    Campus Safety    Contact Us    Support our Students         Contact   1200 West Harrison St., 3010 SSB  Chicago, IL 60607  Phone: (312) 996-7140  studentaffairs@uic.edu        Social Media Accounts    Facebook    Twitter    Instagram    YouTube             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Pr